    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your divinity spills out from you in a visible aura, either blessing your allies or throwing off your foes. You're continuously surrounded by a @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.XSujb7EsSwKl19Uu] or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.7ZinJNzxq0XF0oMx] spell (your choice), with a spell rank equal to half your level rounded up. The radius is 15 feet, and you can't increase it; instead, if you Sustain the Spell, you can change it from bless to bane or vice versa. You can Dismiss the spell; if you do, or if the spell ends for another reason, it returns automatically after 1 minute.</p><hr /><p><em>Note: The Pathfinder 2e system does not currently support auras that require saving throws, so only the bless aura is automated.</em></p>",
